\pard\sa100\li360\fi-240\f0\fs23 - Implement preset expansion in one place. Do not scatter preset expansion through model code.\par
\pard\sa100\li360\fi-240\f0\fs23 - Add validation for invalid combinations. DENSE must reject compact geometry fields unless they are unset or explicitly conventional.\par
\pard\sa100\li360\fi-240\f0\fs23 - Record requested preset and resolved module geometries in run metadata.\par
\pard\sa100\li360\fi-240\f0\fs23 - Add checkpoint metadata fields for compact identity, dimensions, head metadata, and resolved orders.\par
\pard\sa100\li360\fi-240\f0\fs23 - Add hard-fail resume checks for missing or mismatched metadata.\par
\pard\sa120\sb170\f0\fs24\b Tests\b0\par
\pard\sa100\li360\fi-240\f0\fs23 - Preset expansion tests.\par
\pard\sa100\li360\fi-240\f0\fs23 - Explicit module override tests.\par
\pard\sa100\li360\fi-240\f0\fs23 - Invalid combination tests.\par
\pard\sa100\li360\fi-240\f0\fs23 - Save/resume metadata match and mismatch tests.\par
\pard\sa120\sb170\f0\fs24\b Exit gate\b0\par
