\pard\sa100\li360\fi-240\f0\fs23 - Tiny CHEBY_MLP_BLOCK train-step smoke test.\par
\pard\sa120\sb170\f0\fs24\b Exit gate\b0\par
\pard\sa170\f0\fs23 CHEBY_MLP_BLOCK runs and can be compared directly against CHEBY_CURVE.\par

\pard\sa190\sb280\f0\fs29\b 9. Stage 6: HEAD_AWARE_BLOCK and BLOCK\b0\par
\pard\sa120\sb170\f0\fs24\b Goal\b0\par
\pard\sa170\f0\fs23 Implement head-aware attention compaction and then expose BLOCK as the convenience preset combining it with MLP_BLOCK.\par
\pard\sa120\sb170\f0\fs24\b Q/K/V layout\b0\par
\pard\sa180\li360\f1\fs20 C_role[head, depth_order, head_out_order, input_order]\line W_role,l,h[o,i] = sum_pqr C_role[h,p,q,r] * D[l,p] * HeadOut[o,q] * Input[i,r]\par
\pard\sa120\sb170\f0\fs24\b Attention output layout\b0\par
\pard\sa180\li360\f1\fs20 C_out[head, depth_order, output_order, head_in_order]\line W_o,l[o,h,i] = sum_pqr C_out[h,p,q,r] * D[l,p] * Output[o,q] * HeadIn[i,r]\par
\pard\sa120\sb170\f0\fs24\b Work items\b0\par
\pard\sa100\li360\fi-240\f0\fs23 - Implement attention_geometry=head_aware_block as an explicit module geometry.\par
